#

Lamb Chops with Mint Chimichurri

$35
750 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-Free

Tags:

GourmetDinnerMeatGluten-Free

Description

Succulent sous vide lamb chops paired with a refreshing mint chimichurri and a side of perfectly roasted root vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Lamb chops: 4 pieces
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 2, minced
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Salt and pepper: to taste
  • Carrots: 2, sliced
  • Parsnips: 2, sliced
  • Beets: 2, sliced
  • Potatoes: 2, quartered
  • Mint leaves: 1 cup, packed
  • Fresh parsley: 1/2 cup, packed
  • Red wine vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • Red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Shallot: 1, finely chopped
  • Lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
